e back when others were not.  You complimented me in that post and it stuck with me.  In every post since then you have sounded reasonable and logical; your opinions have always been worthy of admiration even when I disagree with the fundamental premise of them. Of everyone in Legion, I had expected a different response from you than the one you gave today:<br>
